Note:
Runa Security Library: Distributed Audit Consensus Module

Production-grade distributed consensus system for security audit trails providing
Byzantine fault tolerance, cryptographic integrity, and multi-party verification.
Implements advanced consensus algorithms including Raft, PBFT, and custom hybrid
protocols. Surpasses Hyperledger Fabric, Tendermint, and enterprise blockchain
solutions with enhanced security audit capabilities.

Features:
- Byzantine Fault Tolerant consensus for security events
- Cryptographically verifiable audit trail consensus
- Multi-node distributed audit log replication
- Automatic conflict resolution and consistency maintenance
- Real-time consensus monitoring and health checking
- Adaptive consensus algorithm selection based on network conditions
- Cross-organization audit trail synchronization
- Tamper-evident distributed ledger for security events
:End Note

Import "collections" as Collections
Import "datetime/datetime" as DateTime
Import "crypto/hash" as Hash
Import "crypto/signatures" as Signatures
Import "security/primitives/audit" as Audit
Import "networking/core" as Network

